rsense installation refer to http://cx4a.org/software/rsense/manual.html
lack of $RSENSE_HOME/lib/rsense.jar, it can be found at https://github.com/Samsinite/rsense.git/vendor/rsense-0.3/lib/rsense.jar

airline; powerline font
1 现成的字体下载后在Terminal中选择:
    https://github.com/powerline/fonts
    Terminal->Preferences->font->Anonymous Pro for Powerline Bold
2 对目前的字体打补丁，就是不改变Terminal字体，把powerline的6个符号打补丁打进现在的字体里:
    https://www.zhihu.com/question/36593223
    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/19105279/how-can-i-setup-my-vim-airline-or-vim-powerline
    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3359/how-do-i-fix-the-status-bar-symbols-in-the-airline-plugin

